      "section_id": "s4",
      "section_path": [
        "The European Commission",
        "Substance"
      ],
      "ordinal": 35,
      "text": "We believe – as partly shared in the preparatory work for this initiative – that existing consumer protection rules will need to be addressed more clearly.",
